IMAPStore personal-remote
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
User yasser.kaddoura19@gmail.com
AuthMechs XOAUTH2
PassCmd "$HOME/.config/mutt/scripts/oauth2tool personal"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore personal-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/mail/personal/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/personal/INBOX
Flatten .

Channel personal
Expunge Both
Far :personal-remote:
Near :personal-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
SyncState *
MaxMessages 0
ExpireUnread no
